This paper deals with image in-painting using neural networks, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the robustness of the network, which is a common topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The methodology used in the paper involves testing and evaluating the network's performance, which is related to neural networks (cs.NE) and multimedia (cs.MM).
